  "reference_number": "INU0335",
  "remarks": "\nMachine Sazi Arak is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Machine Sazi Arak is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting, or facilitating, a relevant nuclear activity, namely the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran; or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran. \n",
